title: Neela Aakash
subTitle: Neela and Akash fall in love with each other after a comedy of errors. But her drunkard father disapproves of their union as she is the sole breadwinner of their family.

title: Himmat
subTitle: Raghu, a reformed criminal, rescues a woman and soon their love blossoms into a happy marriage. However, when the police arrive to catch him in connection with a murder, their lives turn upside down.

title: Hip Hip Hurray
subTitle: Sandeep, an engineer, takes up the temporary job of a sports teacher in a school. However, he gets confronted by the principal and is forced to prove his mettle despite all odds.

title: Baadshah
subTitle: An amateur detective, Raj, goes by the nickname of Baadshah. But this name soon causes a misunderstanding that lands him in the middle of a conspiracy to assassinate the chief minister of Goa.

title: Besharam
subTitle: Babli is a small-time thief who steals cars in order to support a noble cause. His life takes an interesting turn when he falls in love with Tara and decides to mend his ways.

title: Shor
subTitle: Deepak, a young boy, loses his ability to speak due to a tragic accident. His heartbroken father, Shankar, works hard in order to treat him, but remains unaware of the fate awaiting him.

title: Maang Bharo Sajana
subTitle: Chandra, a college student, loves Gita and wishes to marry her. When Gita's father discovers this, he rejects his proposal claiming that Chandra is not the biological son of his mother Sita.

title: Mere Hamdam Mere Dost
subTitle: A young man falls in love with a rich heiress posing as a poor girl. Appalled by her deception, he severs ties with her. Soon he learns the shocking truth behind his father's death.

title: Naseeb
subTitle: The lives of friends Namdev, Raghu, Damu and Jaggi take a turn for the worse when they win a lottery. Raghu and Damu murder Jaggi and frame Namdev who later returns to seek revenge.

title: Meri Awaaz Suno
subTitle: Officer Kumar pursues a gang targeting women, risking his and his family's lives as he strives to bring the kidnappers to justice in a high-stakes operation.

title: Meri Awaaz Suno
subTitle: Officer Kumar pursues a gang targeting women, risking his and his family's lives as he strives to bring the kidnappers to justice in a high-stakes operation.

title: Hanste Zakhm
subTitle: Mahendru, a widowed police officer, lives with his young daughter Chanda. Through a series of circumstances, he is forced to care for Chanda's best friend, Rekha, who is a prostitute's daughter.

title: Love
subTitle: Prithvi and Maggie fall in love and decide to tie the knot. However, trouble knocks the paradise when Stella, Maggie's mother, objects their match due to his criminal past.

title: Chitchor
subTitle: When Geeta's sister arranges her wedding with a young engineer, their father mistakenly brings the wrong man home. However, as love blossoms between the two, the arrival of a letter startles everyone.

title: Raaste Kaa Patthar
subTitle: Jai, who lets his employer and superiors use his apartment for sordid trysts, falls in love with Nita, his employer's fiancee.

title: Heer Ranjha
subTitle: Heer, who belongs to a rich family, and Ranjha, a poor farm boy, fall madly in love with each other. But, their lives take a tragic turn when Heer's parents forcibly marry her off to a wealthy man.

title: Bandhan
subTitle: Dharamchand, a righteous man, hates his father Jeevanlal as he stole to make ends meet. However, things take a turn when Dharamchand is accused of his father's murder.

title: Ganga Tere Desh Mein
subTitle: After arresting and institutionalising a notorious criminal who has lost his mental faculties, inspector Ajay finds his mother feeding the criminal. But when he digs deeper he uncovers a tragic truth.

title: Andhaa Kanoon
subTitle: When his parents are killed by three men, Amar, Akbar and Anthony, Vijay teams up with a forest officer who was framed in a murder case to avenge their deaths.

title: Itihaas
subTitle: Naina, who is betrothed to an influential man, falls in love and elopes with Karan, the son of an employee of her fiance. Soon, bounty hunters start hunting the duo to claim a hefty reward.

title: Itihaas
subTitle: Naina, who is betrothed to an influential man, falls in love and elopes with Karan, the son of an employee of her fiance. Soon, bounty hunters start hunting the duo to claim a hefty reward.

title: Aghaat
subTitle: Madhav is a noble union representative who faces opposition from Rustom, a vile man, in a bid to register the most members. When an employee loses his legs, Rustom's abhorrent antics test Madhav.

title: Bandini
subTitle: Devendra, a doctor working at a women's prison, falls for Kalyani, a convicted prisoner. However, things become complicated as the tale behind her crimes unfolds.

title: Ek Nari Ek Brahmachari
subTitle: Raj lives with his brother, Mohan, who has taken a vow of celibacy. Trouble brews when Neena, along with her son, walks into their house and claims that Mohan is the father of her child.

title: Apne Apne
subTitle: Ravi gets married to Sharda against his mother's wish. However, when Sharda suffers a miscarriage and leaves Ravi, he marries Seema, a rich woman.

title: Samadhi
subTitle: Lakhan Singh gives up his life of crime when he falls in love and marries Champa. However, things take a turn when she falls sick and he is forced to become a criminal again.

title: Mulzim
subTitle: A farmer wants to build a hospital in his village, but is at odds with a landlord who wants to build a theatre on the same land. To get him out of the way, the landlord frames the farmer for murder.

title: Ittefaq
subTitle: Dev Verma, a police officer, gets trapped in a web of lies when he interrogates two witnesses who also happen to be the prime suspects in a double homicide.

title: Ganwaar
subTitle: Gopal, the son of a generous landlord, disguises himself as an illiterate villager to protect the villagers from the cruel Vijay Bahadur, the brother of his step-mother.
